  16 Dec 2012; Sergei Trofimovich <slyfox@gentoo.org>
  +files/pandoc-1.9.4.5-disable-writes-other-man.patch,
  -files/pandoc-1.9.1.2-haddock-2.10.0.patch, -files/pandoc-1.9.3-ghc-7.5.patch,
